tutorial: How to set up a new Chart
type: Adding Charts - Why is it blank?

definition.text: Woohoo, you did it! You have added your first custom chart.

paragraphs.text: However, at this point, your chart is pretty boring.
If you check the Charting Space, your Time Machine is there, but it is totally blank. That’s because we haven’t hooked it up to any of your data.
